game.description:
Cinderella is happy for her pregnancy and a new baby who is about to come to her life. However, she needs to go through one last health check-up before entering the last month of pregnancy. Since you have good doctor skills, you have accepted the responsibility of taking her to a doctor to check out her temperature and pulse rate. Are you ready to play this important role and surprise the world with your ultimate medical skills? Join Cinderella Pregnant Check Up game right now and meet with the beautiful character!

In this brand new doctor game for girls, you will be able to learn a number of important things about how to take care of a pregnant woman during the most crucial days of her life. This free online allows you to learn how to see the baby using the proper usage of ultrasound machine and check out the actual condition of baby in the Cinderella tummy. After completing the check-up process, you also have to take care of arranging some music and belly tattoos to make her feel relaxed. 

We are sure that you are going to play this one of the best doctor games for girls again and again in your browser to have a lot fun and joy. Apply all the tools you see on the screen to conduct the full check-up of Cinderella and her unborn child. The girl relies on your skills, so go ahead to perform your job perfectly and have a blast. Explore more doctor games on our website to learn how to treat other important diseases with the right precautions. We also maintain a finest range of surgical games for kids here.
